  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "He fell and died on his way home from the gas station",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Halawatha Police say that a mechanic who was returning to his home after waiting in a fuel queue in Halawatha area for several days suddenly fell ill and died in Munneswaram area of \u200b\u200bHalawatha Kurunagala road.",
        "A 37-year-old father of two named Prasanna Fernando, resident of Halawata, Rambepitiya, has died.",
        "Police say that on the 12th, on the news that fuel was coming to Halawata, he rode his motorcycle for over 10 kilometers and spent the long queue at the fuel station, but fell down and died on the side of the road in Munneswaram area due to lack of fuel."
      ],
